### Home-page widgets (`HOME_PAGE_WIDGETS`)

Tabbar and navbar live on **Main/home** — same as preview scripts (`tabbar: 'Main'`, `navbar: 'Main'`).

```
navigateToWidget('tabbar' | 'navbar')
  → ensure on home (back if needed)
  → wait ~mobile_navbar1_title
  → wait widget sentinel (~mobile_tabbar1 or ~mobile_navbar1_title)
  → style console still uses ~exinput_i on Main
  → NEVER tap ~tabbar_link_caption / ~navbar_link_caption
```

